{"tid":2237942,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"大家憎唔憎成個教育制度","createTime":"2020-10-10T16:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T15:46:00.000Z","uid":209331,"like":61,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"46fe33d1df59025e73edc844476ec7558446e878","tid":2237942,"uid":209331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"由細到大都係填鴨式教育，唔明唔緊要，背曬佢先<br />\n讀書考試又要快又要準，仲要謙虛唔畀驕傲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時候想讀下啲課外書，睇武俠小說睇愛情小說又話對學業冇幫助，好似睇書只係為咗搵錢咁。有時又好奇歷史名人啲事蹟，到上堂嗰陣又淨係背XX變法/改革的N大好處<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有朋友話曾幾何時都好鍾意讀書，而家見到一大堆字就反胃，諗起以前操卷操到癲嘅日子，真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n範文最憎孟子嗰篇 魚我所欲也 熊掌乜乜乜 屌你咁多口水 講埋d垃圾類比當我低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我拍咗條片講 有興趣可以睇吓同subscribe <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RVCc5dRwBbI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRVCc5dRwBbI&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=c0a051c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RVCc5dRwBbI</a>"},{"pid":"432529328016f77ba68f81343a042a0d9ee85232","tid":2237942,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"7df0df37c5aecbeb7fc2a47c9bb67db9c07206eb","tid":2237942,"uid":316674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"絕對"},{"pid":"8e772858664bc3b626565f30556827713e0c0cb0","tid":2237942,"uid":205469,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"睇武俠小說睇愛情小說又話對學業冇幫助<br />\n<br />\n但我當年中學要做金庸武俠小說book report喎<br />\n又要讀 胭脂扣，傾城之戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f227b79db44d9ad57685b7c8ab5